title: #92Noon! Big week for Twins and Vikings!
description: NFL writer Don Banks joins in the 10a hour, and Lavelle is in studio for the entire final hour! The Twins host the Yankees and Vikings training camp starts this week, so a lot to be excited about on a Monday morning!
